data.name: KCCLaunch
data.description:
KCCLaunch Is An Exclusive Decentralized Launchpad Focusing On Low Cap Gems & Meme coins on KuCoin Community Chain. KCCLaunch is the first platform working towards building an ecosystem on KCC for all projects launching on KCC. The project plans to come up with a swap platform. 

KCCLaunch Features:

CURATED PROJECTS:
The KCC Launch team individually vets all prospective projects on our launchpad. Only the best of the best make it to the Public.

GUARANTEED ALLOCATION:
KCC Launch backers receive a guaranteed allocation of project tokens based on their tokens held and lock duration.

STAKING BENEFITS:
Locking your KCCL tokens in the staking contract for longer periods earns higher allocations plus staking rewards.

LOCKED FUNDS:
All IDO project tokens on KCC Launch are placed in a linear vesting contract, so listing dumps will be minimized.

KCCL DAO:
After launch, KCC Launch intends to devolve into a DAO, ceding control of governance to the hands of community.
